data.meta_description:
Collaborating with Brian Eno is like having your very own alchemist in the studio. Almost everything he touches turns to gold.&nbsp;



In the interest of keeping the In Sheep’s Clothing HiFi virtual record collection diverse and not overdoing it with Eno, which is tempting, we’ve opted to create a space dedicated exclusively to our beloved music polymath: a compilation of our favorite Eno albums outside of his solo career, highlighting his gifts as a collaborator, co-writer, producer and musician.&nbsp;
